Mars%20General%20Election%2C%20Draws%20Criticism%20From%20Political%20Parties%2C%20Except%20PML(N)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08190356%2Fimage-1816.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20suspension%20of%20internet%20and%20mobile%20services%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20attributed%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20situation%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20country%20heads%20to%20the%20election%2C%20has%20drawn%20significant%20criticism%20from%20the%20majority%20of%20political%20parties%20and%20civil%20society%20regarding%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20128%20million%20voters%20were%20eligible%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20general%20election%2C%20with%20polling%20stations%20opening%20at%208%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20was%20already%20viewed%20as%20controversial%20with%20a%20series%20of%20conviction%20judgments%20against%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaaf%20leader%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20ensuring%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F8%2F8%2Fformer-pakistan-pm-imran-khan-barred-from-politics-for-5-years%5C%22%3Ewas%20disbarred%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20election.%20It%20is%20widely%20believed%20that%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%E2%80%99s%20(PML-N)%20former%20three-time%20Prime%20Minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20is%20the%20frontrunner%20in%20the%20election.%20He%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20current%20favoured%20candidate%20of%20the%20military%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20polling%20booths%20opened%2C%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20interior%20ministry%20enforced%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20and%20internet%20services%20nationwide%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20concerns%E2%80%9D.%20When%20questioned%20by%20reporters%20at%20a%20polling%20station%2C%20interim%20Prime%20Minister%20Anwaar-ul-Haq%20Kakar%20justified%20the%20measure%20within%20the%20context%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwave%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%9D%20prevailing%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20polling%20day%2C%20Kakar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fanwaar_kakar%2Fstatus%2F1755573370635059510%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Chigh%20voter%20turnout%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20voices%2C%20expressed%20through%20the%20votes%2C%20will%20contribute%20to%20the%20fortification%20of%20our%20democracy%2C%20and%20for%20that%2C%20people%20of%20Pakistan%20deserve%20every%20bit%20of%20appreciation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20and%20internet%20services%20holds%20considerable%20importance%20for%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20election%20process%20as%20it%20could%20potentially%20affect%20voter%20turnout.%20In%20Pakistan%2C%20voters%20rely%20on%20a%20text%20messaging%20service%20provided%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20to%20ascertain%20their%20designated%20polling%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3ECriticising%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20demanding%20its%20immediate%20revocation%2C%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20noted%20that%20it%20has%20occurred%20despite%20the%20provincial%20High%20Court%20of%20Sindh%20directing%20uninterrupted%20internet%20services%20to%20be%20maintained%20on%20voting%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20PTA%20claiming%20it%20has%20received%20no%20instructions%20from%20the%20government%20to%20block%20internet%20services%2C%20there%20is%20a%20worrying%20lack%20of%20transparency%20about%20where%2C%20when%20and%20how%20long%20the%20disruption%20will%20continue%2C%20thereby%20affecting%20voters%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20information%20and%20potentially%20the%20transmission%20of%20results.%20Those%20who%20gave%20this%20order%20must%20be%20identified%20and%20held%20responsible%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(PPP)%20petitioned%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Pakistan%20to%20take%20cognisance%20that%20the%20disruption%20of%20internet%20services%20would%20impact%20voter%20turnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%E2%80%99s%20Central%20Election%20Cell%20in-charge%20Senator%20Taj%20Haider%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20suspend%20mobile%20phone%20services%20on%20grounds%20of%20security%20concerns%20was%20%E2%80%98illegal%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1391859%5C%22%3Eviolated%20a%202018%20court%20order%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20closure%20has%20also%20adversely%20affected%20reporting%20and%20responding%20to%20security%20incidents.%20One%20of%20our%20workers%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20Mirpurkhas%20today%20and%20it%20was%20after%20an%20hour%20that%20we%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20murder%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20stated%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Flive%2Felections-2024%231811985%5C%22%3Eas%20reported%20by%20%3Ci%3EDawn%20News%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20media%20reports%2C%20at%20least%20nine%20people%2C%20including%20six%20security%20personnel%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20violent%20incidents%20reported%20across%20Pakistan%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20also%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20political%20parties%2C%20except%20PML-N%2C%20have%20objected%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20internet%20disruption.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20spite%20of%20our%20request%20to%20ECP%20to%20restore%20services%2C%20these%20services%20have%20not%20restored%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20PPP%20chief%20Bilawal%20Bhutto%20Zardari%20demanded%2C%20through%20his%20X%20account%2C%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmobile%20phone%20services%20must%20be%20restored%20immediately%20across%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20have%20formidable%20online%20presence%20among%20political%20parties%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20suspension%20of%20mobile%20and%20internet%20services%20was%20%E2%80%9Can%20organised%20conspiracy%20to%20deprive%20the%20people%20of%20their%20constitutional%20right%20to%20cast%20their%20vote%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20shutting%20down%20mobile%20phone%20services%20is%20to%20prevent%20evidence%20of%20rigging%20at%20polling%20stations%20from%20coming%20to%20the%20fore.%20The%20nation%20will%20not%20accept%20such%20systematic%20rigging%20attempts%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20polls%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20PTI%20spokesman%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Flive-blog%2F37%23pti-terms-suspension-of-mobile-internet-services-an-organised-conspiracy%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EThe%20Express%20Tribune%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20accused%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20of%20failing%20to%20maintain%20the%20transparency%20and%20credibility%20of%20the%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PML-N%2C%20which%20is%20favoured%20to%20win%20the%20elections%2C%20maintained%20a%20conspicuous%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20article%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20polling%20day%2C%20Nighat%20Dad%2C%20a%20Pakistani%20lawyer%2C%20who%20runs%20an%20NGO%20Digital%20Rights%20Foundation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenews.com.pk%2Fprint%2F1155503-the-net-must-go-on%5C%22%3Ehad%20written%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20shutdowns%20would%20not%20only%20stop%20effective%20reporting%20by%20journalists%2C%20but%20would%20also%20%E2%80%9Cimpede%20key%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20national%20and%20international%20election%20observers%2C%20political%20candidates%2C%20and%20civil%20society%20members%2C%20from%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20electoral%20proceedings%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20earlier%2C