ters%2C%20MLAs%2C%20and%20MPs%20converged%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20February%207%2C%20over%20the%20non-payment%20of%20dues%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgross%20injustice%E2%80%9D%20being%20meted%20out%20by%20tax%20devolution%20formula%20by%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20Kannadigas%2C%20pay%20taxes%20of%20Rs%20430%2C000%20crore.%20But%20we%20receive%20only%20Rs%2050%2C000%20crore%20back.%20That%20means%20out%20of%20every%20Rs%20100%2C%20only%20Rs%2013%20comes%20back%20to%20us.%20Can%20there%20be%20greater%20injustice%20than%20this%3F%20Should%20we%20tolerate%20this%20injustice%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Siddaramaiah%20at%20the%20protest.%20%E2%80%9CInjustice%20with%20regard%20to%20tax%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%2062%2C098%20crore%20has%20been%20done%20to%20the%20state%20by%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission.%20Shouldn%E2%80%99t%20we%20question%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%2015th%20Finance%20Commission%20is%20a%20constitutional%20body%2C%20and%20its%20primary%20function%20is%20to%20recommend%20the%20distribution%20of%20tax%20proceeds%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20states%2C%20as%20well%20as%20among%20the%20states%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Union%20finance%20minister%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20denied%20the%20accusations%20levelled%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress-led%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20a%20%E2%80%98separatist%E2%80%99%20mindset%20and%20is%20spreading%20a%20%E2%80%98false%20narrative%E2%80%99%20about%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20discrimination%20against%20the%20state%20in%20fund%20allocation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%20hit%20out%20at%20Sitharaman%E2%80%99s%20statement.%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Priyank%20Kharge%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%2014th%20Finance%20Commission%2C%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20devolution%20was%204.71%25%2C%20which%20has%20now%20been%20reduced%20to%203.65%25%20under%20the%2015th%20Finance%20Commission.%20Our%20government%20is%20losing%20Rs%2073%2C000%20crore%20every%20year.%20We%E2%80%99re%20not%20receiving%20GST%20reimbursement%2C%20MNREGA%20payments%20from%20the%20central%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FpYnYZpRbKRM%3Fsi%3DyRhT5jgpLOtoP9H9%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EKharge%20further%20alleged%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20announcing%20budgets%20for%20us%20but%20has%20not%20given%20a%20single%20penny%20to%20our%20government.%E2%80%9D%20According%20to%20the%20Karnataka%20government%2C%20it%20has%20invited%20all%20the%20MLAs%20and%20MPs%2C%20including%20the%20ones%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20state%20stands%20as%20one%20to%20press%20for%20its%20demands.%20However%2C%20Congress%20leaders%20say%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20gave%20the%20protest%20amiss.%20Out%20of%2026%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%2025%20are%20held%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20one%20more%20by%20its%20alliance%2C%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20tried%20approaching%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20to%20highlight%20the%20issue%20to%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20spokesperson%20Bhavya%20Narasimhamurthy%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20approached%20them%20several%20times%2C%20we%20have%20even%20invited%20them%20here%20because%20we%