ate.%20May%2010%2C%202021%20was%20the%20day%20the%20new%20chief%20minister%2C%20Sarma%2C%20was%20sworn%20in%20after%20the%20BJP%20won%20the%20state%20assembly%20elections%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20replacing%20the%20incumbent%20chief%20minister%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CrossCurrent%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fassam-himanta-biswa-sarma-public-money-helicopter-chartered-flights-bjp-party-wedding%5C%22%3Ejoint%20report%20based%20on%20the%20partial%20RTI%20reply%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Sarma%20government%20showed%20that%20the%20state%20government%20had%20spent%20crores%20in%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20non-governmental%20activities%20%E2%80%93%20which%20included%20attending%20high%20profile%20weddings%20within%20and%20outside%20Assam%20and%20engaging%20in%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20work%20including%20campaigning%20for%20party%20leaders%20and%20its%20allies%20by%20violating%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20model%20code%20of%20conduct.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20responded%20to%20the%20RTI%20based%20report%20by%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Chit%20job%E2%80%9D%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20paid%20for%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20non-governmental%20work%2C%20it%20could%20not%20produce%20any%20proof%20of%20it%20immediately.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20RTI%20reply%20of%20the%20Sarma%20government%2C%20furthermore%2C%20bore%20the%20facts%20which%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fassam-cmo-says-expenses-for-party-work-are-paid-for-by-the-political-party-but-rti-details-dont-bear-that-out%5C%22%3Epublished%20in%20response%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20CMO%E2%80%99s%20statement%2