air-minded%20watch%20dogs%20filmed%20this%20gentleman%E2%80%99s%20questionable%20conduct.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20video%20released%20by%20the%20channel%2C%20Masih%20can%20be%20seen%20picking%20and%20choosing%20ballot%20papers%2C%20marking%20eight%20and%20then%20dropping%20these%20in%20a%20tray.%20As%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20eight%20invalid%20votes%20%E2%80%93%20all%20cast%20for%20the%20AAP%2FCongress%20candidates%20%E2%80%93%20were%20knocked%20out%2C%20leading%20the%20BJP%20to%20win.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInevitably%2C%20the%20matter%20went%20to%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAstounded%20by%20videographed%20shenanigans%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwont-allow-democracy-to-be-murdered-cji-chandrachud-on-chandigarh-stolen-mayoral-election%5C%22%3EChief%20Justice%20called%20this%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmockery%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmurder%E2%80%9D%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdemocracy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stating%20further%20that%20the%20presiding%20officer%20ought%20to%20be%20prosecuted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20may%20recall%20how%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20a%20long%20chat%20with%20an%20election%20officer%20in%20Georgia%20during%20the%20US%20Presidential%20election%20of%202020%2C%20nudging%20him%20gently%20and%20otherwise%20to%20produce%20just%20an%20additional%2011%2C000%20or%20so%20votes%20to%20ensure%20his%20victory%20in%20Georgia.%20Alas%2C%20that%20man%20with%20a%20law-abiding%2C%20democratic%20conscience%20did%20not%20oblige.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAW_Bdf_jGaA%3Fsi%3DvkPpRhuVzK5v4TMI%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20do%20not%20know%20as%20of%20now%20if%20Anil%20Masih%20in%20Chandigarh%20was%20acting%20on%20his%20own%20loyal%20volition%20or%20whether%20a%20call%20had%20gone%20out%20to%20him%20from%20the%20top%2C%20as%20it%20had%20in%20Georgia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecall%20the%20time%20when%20a%20former%20prime%20minister%20from%20the%20very%20same%20ruling%20party%20as%20now%20lost%20a%20government%20at%20the%20centre%20in%20New%20Delhi%20by%20one%2C%20repeat%20one%2C%20vote%20rather%20than%20resorting%20to%20any%20subterfuge%20to%20prevent%20such%20a%20dethronement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20was%20then.%20Now%20even%20a%20measly%20mayoral%20contest%20with%20all%20of%2036%20votes%20in%20the%20reckoning%20must%20be%20won%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20it%20takes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20citizens%20who%20still%20stand%20by%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20and%20fair%20elections%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20basic%20bedrock%20of%20democracy%20must%20wish%20to%20hear%20from%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20the%20Chandigarh%20happening%2C%20especially%20in%20view%20of%20what%20the%20top%20court%20has%20had%20to%20say.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWide%20sections%20also%20speculate%20whether%20the%20Chandigarh%20%E2%80%98murder%20of%20democracy%E2%80%99%20may%20not%20after%20all%20be%20a%20preview%20of%20%E2%80%98slaughter%E2%80%99%20on%20a%20larger%20scale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDo%20let%20us%20remember%20that%20a%20defining%20General%20Election%20for%20parliament%20is%20due%20in%20less%20than%20three%20months%2C%20and%20Modi%20has%20already%2C%20more%20than%20once%2C%20announced%20the%20things%20slated%20to%20happen%20in%20his%20%E2%80%9Cthird%20term%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESuch%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eapriori%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eself-assurance%20seems%20both%20democratically%20unlovely%20and%20rather%20ominous%2C%20given%20the%20shameless%20transgression%20in%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20all%2C%20some%20pollsters%2C%20among%20them%20those%20that%20tend%20to%20favour%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20have%20proffered%20the%20calculation%20that%20the%20exit%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar%20from%20the%20IND%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ealliance%20is%20set%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Edamage%20the%20ruling%20combine%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Esubstantially%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3EBihar%20rather%20than%20add%20to%20its%20fortun%3C%2Fspan%3Ees%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20once%2C%20the%20disgust%20expressed%20by%20common%20Biharis%20is%20unreserved%20and%20bad%20news%20for%20those%20who%20brought%20about%20this%20latest%20unconscionably%20comical%20coup.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESame%20with%20the%20roughshod%20happenings%20in%20Jharkhand.%20There%20too%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20JMM%20seem%20well%20poised%20to%20win%20most%20of%20the%2014%20parliamentary%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20resentment%20of%20the%20Adivasis%2C%20both%20Sarna%20and%20Christian%2C%20must%20be%20heard%20to%20be%20believed%2C%20as%20also%20the%20welcome%20they%20gave%20the%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20raids%20by%20teams%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20morning%20of%20February%206%20on%20a%20slew%20of%20personnel%20associated%20with%20the%20ruling%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20in%20the%20Capital%20surfaced%20as%20the%20morning%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebaddi%20khabar%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20big%20news%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esome%20media%20channels%20also%20made%20bold%20to%20feature%20a%20simultaneous%20press%20conference%20by%20Atishi%20Singh%2C%20minister%20in%20the%20Kejriwal%20cabinet%2C.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20her%20briefing%2C%20she%20accused%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20of%20violating%20Supreme%20Court%20guidelines%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20its%20investigations.%20The%20ED%20has%20strenuously%20denied%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20charges%20but%20the%20popular%20perception%20that%20what%20the%20agency%20is%20overseeing%20the%20%E2%80%98Enforcement%E2%80%99%20of%20is%20Dictatorship.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDemocracy%20already%20having%20been%20murdered%2C%20as%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20said%20in%20open%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImagine%20how%20fraught%20a%20mere%20D%20can%20be.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbadri-raina%5C%22%3EBadri%20Raina%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707375039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08121514%2FUntitled-design-4-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmurder-of-democracy-supreme-court-chandigarh-narendra-modi-anil-massih%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Modi%20speaking%20of%20a%20third%20term%20seems%20both%20democratically%20unlovely%20and%20rather%20ominous%2C%20given%20the%20shameless%20transgression%20in%20Chandigarh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmurder-of-democracy-supreme-court-chandigarh-narendra-modi-anil-massih%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20'Jai%20Shri%20Ram'%20Slogans%20and%20Temple%20Talk%2C%20Hindutva%20Dominates%20UP%20Assembly%20Session%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08114352%2FScreenshot-2024-02-08-at-11.43.13-AM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20budget%20session%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20assembly%20has%20been%20dominated%20by%20Hindutva%20this%20season%3A%20passing%20a%20resolution%20congratulating%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%3B%20the%20repeated%20raising%20of%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20slogans%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MLAs%3B%20and%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20defence%20of%20the%20fight%20to%20claim%20mosques%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20enjoys%20an%20overwhelming%20majority%20in%20the%20state%20and%20is%20comfortably%20placed%20electorally.%20Yet%20it%20has%20not%20shied%20away%20from%20unleashing%20its%20core%20agenda%20of%20Hindutva%20and%20raking%20up%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20of%20the%20past%20to%20target%20the%20Opposition%20Samajwadi%20Party%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20woo%20Hindu%20voters%2C%20who%20form%20three-fourths%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20February%207%2C%20Adityanath%2C%20while%20speaking%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%2C%20minced%20no%20words%20in%20indicating%20the%20intent%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Right%20in%20claiming%20the%20two%20remaining%20mosques%20in%20the%20Hindutva%20agenda%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Shahi%20Eidgah%20Masjid%20in%20Mathura%20and%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20in%20Varanasi%20%E2%80%93%20where%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20claim%20grand%20temples%20stood%2C%20dedicated%20to%20Lord%20Krishna%20and%20Lord%20Shiva%2C%20before%20they%20were%20destroyed%20by%20Mughal%20Emperor%20Aurangzeb.%20While%20the%20matter%20in%20both%20suits%20is%20in%20court%2C%20Adityanath%20made%20a%20cheeky%20reference%20to%20the%20district%20administration%20in%20Varanasi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fvaranasi-district-admin-oversees-hindu-prayers-inside-basement-of-gyanvapi-mosque%5C%22%3Eoverseeing%20Hindu%20puja%20inside%20a%20cellar%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20within%20hours%20of%20a%20local%20court%20controversially%20handing%20over%20the%20basement%20to%20the%20Hindus%20for%20prayer%20on%20January%2031%20and%20breaking%20a%20section%20of%20the%20barricades%20at%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20witnessed%20the%20%3Cem%3Eutsav%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20then%20Nandi%20Baba%20(a%20reference%20to%20Nandi%2C%20the%20bull%20who%20serves%20as%20a%20vehicle%20of%20Lord%20Shiva%20in%20Hindu%20mythology)%20also%20asked%20why%20he%20should%20wait.%20Without%20waiting%20any%20longer%2C%20he%20broke%20the%20barricades%20in%20the%20night.%20And%20how%20is%20our%20Krishna%20Kanhaiya%20going%20to%20relent%3F%E2%80%9D%20Adityanath%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22What%20Does%20'Integral%20Humanism'%20Really%20Mean%20to%20the%20BJP%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-does-integral-humanism-really-mean-to-the-bjp%5C%22%3EWhat%20Does%20%E2%80%98Integral%20Humanism%E2%80%99%20Really%20Mean%20to%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20also%20narrated%20an%20episode%20from%20the%20epic%20%3Cem%3EMahabharata%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20justify%20the%20push%20to%20build%20grand%20temples%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Mathura%20and%20Varanasi%20in%20place%20of%20existing%20mosques.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20built%20at%20the%20site%20where%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20stood%20till%201992%2C%20has%20been%20opened%20to%20the%20public%20and%20legal%20battles%20by%20the%20Hindu%20right%20to%20dispossess%20Muslims%20from%20Mughal-era%20mosques%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura%20have%20intensified%2C%20Adityanath%20alluded%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinevitability%E2%80%9D%20of%20war%20if%20a%20timely%20compromise%20was%20not%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20compared%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinjustice%E2%80%9D%20faced%20by%20the%20Pandavas%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahabharata%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20the%20alleged%20neglect%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura%2C%20where%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E-led%20Hindu%20right%20has%20for%20decades%20claimed%20that%20temples%20were%20demolished%20by%20Mughal%20emperors%20to%20build%20mosques%2C%20under%20previous%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Pandavas%20and%20the%20Kauravas%20were%20at%20the%20brink%20of%20war%2C%20Lord%20Krishna%20went%20to%20the%20Kauravas%20with%20a%20proposal%20of%20compromise%20and%20peace%20to%20avert%20the%20bloody%20conflict.%20Krishna%20proposed%20to%20Duryodhana%2C%20the%20eldest%20of%20the%20Kauravas%2C%20that%20if%20they%20agreed%20to%20give%20just%20five%20villages%20from%20their%20kingdom%20to%20the%20Pandavas%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20need%20for%20war.%20However%2C%20Duryodhana%20refused%20and%20arrogantly%20remarked%20that%20he%20would%20not%20even%20part%20with%20the%20land%20the%20size%20of%20a%20needle.%20The%20two%20sides%20eventually%20fought%20the%20great%20war%20Mahabharata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Mahabharata%20war%20was%20thus%20inevitable.%20And%20what%20happened%3F%20The%20entire%20Kauravas%20were%20annihilated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adityanath%20said%2C%20while%20delivering%20a%20vote%20of%20thanks%20speech%20during%20the%20budget%20session%20of%20the%20UP%20assembly.%20His%20statement%20was%20met%20with%20thunderous%20applause%20and%20chants%20of%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20from%20BJP%20MLAs%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20analogy%20of%20seeking%20%E2%80%9Conly%20five%20villages%E2%80%9D%20to%20prevent%20a%20bloody%20war%2C%20Adityanath%20in%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20Ayodhya-Kashi-Mathura%20campaign%20of%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%2C%20said%20that%20Hindu%20society%20was%20only%20talking%20of%20three%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20society%20here%20has%20for%20centuries%20only%20spoken%20of%20three%20places%20(Ayodhya%2C%20Mathura%20and%20Varanasi).%20We%20only%20asked%20for%20three%20places.%20There%20was%20no%20issue%20about%20other%20places%2C%E2%80%9D%20Adityanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20subject%20to%20interpretation%20to%20conclude%20whether%20Adityanath%20was%20supporting%20the%20claim%20of%20Hindu%20groups%20on%20other%20mosques%20and%20Islamic%20monuments%20beyond%20Ayodhya%2C%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura%20or%20simply%20saying%20that%20the%20Hindu%20Right%E2%80%99s%20demand%20would%20be%20restricted%20to%20these%20three%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UP%20chief%20minister%20further%20said%20that%20Hindus%20wanted%20the%20three%20specific%20sites%20(in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura)%20because%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20are%20special%20places%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20ordinary.%20They%20are%20the%20land%20of%20the%20lord%E2%80%99s%20incarnation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stage%20for%20high-pitched%20Hindutva%20was%20set%20on%20the%20inaugural%20day%20of%20the%20session%20on%20February%202%2C%20when%20Governor%20Anandiben%20Patel%20started%20her%20address%20by%20hailing%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20and%20referred%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20long%20wait%20of%20500%20years%E2%80%9D%20for%20it%20and%20said%20that%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20would%20strengthen%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20Ram%20Rajya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22At%20the%20Heart%20of%20the%20Soundtrack%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20that%20Spreads%20Hateful%20Anti-Minority%20Messages%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsoundtrack-hindutva-minority-messages-kunal-purohit-h-pop%5C%22%3EAt%20the%20Heart%20of%20the%20Soundtrack%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20that%20Spreads%20Hateful%20Anti-Minority%20Messages%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%205%2C%20finance%20and%20parliamentary%20affairs%20minister%20Suresh%20Khanna%20introduced%20a%20resolution%20in%20the%20assembly%20to%20congratulate%20Modi%20and%20Adityanath%20for%20scripting%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20history%E2%80%9D%20by%20installing%20the%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20after%20a%20wait%20of%20500%20years.%20Though%20Khanna%20did%20mention%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20through%20its%20judgment%20in%202019%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ebadhai%20prastav%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20was%20dedicated%20to%20Modi%20and%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20biggest%20event%20of%20the%20century%20due%20to%20which%20we%20have%20found%20our%20pride%20after%20so%20many%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khanna%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20temple%20would%20not%20only%20%E2%80%9Cstrengthen%20social%20and%20cultural%20nationalism%E2%80%9D%20but%20also%20provide%20a%20boost%20to%20the%20tourism%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20senior%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MLAs%20including%20Lalji%20Verma%20objected%20to%20the%20resolution%2C%20asking%2C%20what%20was%20the%20need%20to%20congratulate%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20when%20the%20temple%20was%20being%20constructed%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20court.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EKis%20baat%20ki%20badhai%3F%20Zabardasti%20badhai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(What%20is%20are%20these%20forced%20congratulations%20for)%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20Opposition%20MLA%20was%20heard%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20BJP%20MLAs%20started%20raising%20slogans%2C%20assembly%20speaker%20Satish%20Mahana%20intervened%20and%20requested%20them%20to%20not%20force%20anyone.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20force%20anyone%20to%20congratulate%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahana%20said.%20In%20response%20to%20this%2C%20BJP%20MLAs%20chanted%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20slogans.%20They%20raised%20the%20slogans%20again%20a%20few%20seconds%20later%20when%20the%20assembly%20passed%20the%20resolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUP%20has%20403%20MLAs%20and%20out%20of%20this%20only%2014%2C%20all%20Opposition%20party%20MLAs%2C%20opposed%20the%20motion.%20While%20the%20SP%20has%20108%20MLAs%2C%20its%20ally%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20has%20nine.%20The%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20277%20seats%2C%20way%20more%20than%20the%20half-way%20mark%20required%20to%20be%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%2014%20MLAs%20objecting%20to%20the%20motion%20provided%20the%20BJP%20fresh%20fodder%20to%20play%20its%20Hindutva%20card%20as%20some%20of%20its%20MLAs%2C%20including%20Shalabh%20Mani%20Tripathi%2C%20former%20media%20advisor%20to%20Adityanath%2C%20demanded%20that%20the%20names%20of%20these%2014%20be%20made%20public.%20Such%20was%20the%20pressure%20to%20align%20with%20the%20dominant%20narrative%20that%20on%20February%206%2C%20when%20SP%20MLA%20Swami%20Omvesh%2C%20himself%20a%20saffron-clad%20leader%20like%20Adityanath%2C%20rose%20to%20speak%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20he%20issued%20an%20apologetic%20clarification%20that%20he%20was%20wrongly%20accused%20of%20raising%20his%20hand%20against%20the%20resolution%20on%20Ram%20Mandir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20chant%20the%20Lord%E2%80%99s%20name%20everyday%20after%20performing%20havan%20for%20Shri%20Ram%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Omvesh%2C%20requesting%20the%20House%20to%20clear%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%207%2C%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20long%20speech%20was%20dominated%20by%20references%20to%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20consecration%20ceremony%2C%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20including%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swamyamsevak%20Sangh%20and%20the%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20since%201984%2C%20fulfilment%20of%20the%20promise%20of%20building%20a%20temple%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20invaders%E2%80%9D%20who%20destroyed%20places%20of%20worship%20of%20Hindus%20and%20the%20alleged%20neglect%20of%20Ayodhya%20under%20previous%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20for%20the%20first%20time%20we%20witnessed%20that%20a%20majority%20community%20had%20to%20beg%2C%20even%20when%20public%20faith%20was%20insulted%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22India%E2%80%99s%20RWA%20Uncles%20Are%20Now%20Adding%20to%20the%20Intolerance%20Around%20Us%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findias-rwa-uncles-are-now-adding-to-the-intolerance-around-us%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20RWA%20Uncles%20Are%20Now%20Adding%20to%20the%20Intolerance%20Around%20Us%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Mandir%20dominated%20the%20proceedings%20as%20Speaker%20Mahana%20invited%20all%20members%20of%20the%20assembly%20to%20visit%20the%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20February%2011.%20Samajwadi%20Party%20president%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20refused%20the%20proposal%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20would%20visit%20Ayodhya%20on%20the%20call%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20and%20not%20on%20the%20invitation%20of%20the%20Speaker.%20The%20session%20was%20concluded%20with%20minister%20Khanna%20reading%20out%20a%20lengthy%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Esankalp%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20resolution%2C%20this%20time%20one%20on%20the%20change%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20airport%20from%20Maryada%20Purshottam%20Shri%20Ram%20International%20Airport%20to%20Maharishi%20Valmiki%20International%20Airport%2C%20in%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20strategy%20to%20woo%20Dalits%20through%20Hindutva.%20The%20resolution%20was%20passed%20unanimously%20by%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20resisted%20the%20bait%20and%20avoided%20references%20to%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20or%20countering%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20attacks%20on%20the%20alleged%20neglect%20of%20Ayodhya%2C%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura%2C%20considered%20holy%20by%20Hindus%2C%20under%20the%20previous%20SP%20governments.%20The%20SP%20chief%2C%20who%20is%20trying%20to%20combat%20the%20BJP%20with%20a%20strategy%20of%20mobilising%20the%20PDA%20(OBCs%2C%20Dalits%20and%20minorities)%2C%20dedicated%20his%20speech%20to%20issues%20of%20public%20concern%20and%20livelihood%2C%20such%20as%20inflation%2C%20income%20of%20farmers%2C%20stray%20cattle%20issue%2C%20corruption%2C%20law%20and%20order%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%20and%20unemployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdityanath%20took%20note%20of%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20speech%20and%20criticised%20him%20for%20not%20speaking%20a%20word%20on%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20an%20issue%20of%20national%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20today%2C%20he%20is%20worried%20about%20his%20vote%20bank%20and%20not%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20remains%2C%20for%20how%20long%20can%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20evade%20questions%20around%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20core%20agenda%20of%20Hindutva%20to%20escape%20the%20allegation%2C%20albeit%20bogus%2C%20of%20so-called%20Muslim%20appeasement%3F%20For%20now%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20temple%20politics%20has%20a%20free%20run%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20important%20state%2C%20politically.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707373808000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08114352%2FScreenshot-2024-02-08-at-11.43.13-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwith-jai-shri-ram-slogans-and-temple-talk-hindutva-dominates-up-assembly-session%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Uttar%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Adityanath%20spoke%20at%20length%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bfights%26quot%3B%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Varanasi%20and%20Mathura%20%E2%80%93%20where%20Hindutva%20groups%20have%2C%20or%20want%20to%2C%20take%20over%20mosque%20properties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A21%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwith-jai-shri-ram-s