0from%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20also%20are%20under%20talks%20on%20how%20to%20return%20the%20hundreds%20of%20Myanmar%20security%20personnel%20who%20fled%20into%20Bangladesh%20to%20escape%20the%20fighting%20with%20the%20rebel%20Arakan%20Army.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20far%2C%20until%20today%20as%20many%20as%20338%20people%2C%20mostly%20Myanmar%20border%20security%20guards%20and%20army%20personnel%2C%20had%20entered%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20we%20gave%20them%20shelter%20with%20consultation%20to%20take%20them%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bangladeshi%20minister%20noted%20that%20they%20were%20deliberating%20the%20best%20means%2C%20whether%20by%20sea%20or%20air%2C%20to%20facilitate%20their%20return%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20earlier%2C%20India%20had%20issued%20a%20travel%20advisory%20asking%20all%20citizens%20to%20leave%20Myanmar%E2%80%99s%20Rakhine%20province%20due%20to%20the%20deteriorating%20security%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Rakhine%20State%2C%20the%20military%20junta%20is%20facing%20its%20toughest%20challenge%20after%20the%20Arakan%20Army%2C%20representing%20the%20Rakhine%20ethnic%20minority%2C%20ended%20a%20ceasefire%20last%20November.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20Three%20Brotherhood%20Alliance%2C%20a%20coalition%20of%20ethnic%20minority%20armies%2C%20the%20Arakan%20Army%20launched%20attacks%20on%20border%20outposts%20and%20townships%2C%20achieving%20notable%20victories%20against%20the%20military%2C%20which%20took%20control%20from%20the%20civilian%20government%20in%20February%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMahmud%20also%20met%20with%20his%20counterpart%2C%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20also%20hosted%20a%20dinner%20in%20his%20honour.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37569%2FOfficial_Visit_of_HE_Dr_Hasan_Mahmud_Minister_of_Foreign_Affairs_of_Bangladesh_to_India_February_79_2024%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20MEA%20readout%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20agenda%20for%20discussions%20included%20cross-border%20connectivity%2C%20economic%20and%20development%20partnership%2C%20cooperation%20in%20defence%20and%20security%2C%20power%2C%20energy%2C%20water%20resources%20and%20people-to-people%20exchanges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20expressed%20commitment%20to%20further%20enhance%20their%20collaboration%20to%20promote%20sub-regional%20cooperation%20within%20the%20framework%20of%20BIMSTEC%2C%20IORA%20and%20BBIN%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20MEA%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPleased%20to%20welcome%20Bangladesh%20Foreign%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrHasanMahmud62%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DrHasanMahmud62%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20first%20official%20visit%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussed%20steps%20to%20forge%20ahead%20in%20our%20vibrant%20and%20people-centric%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20exchanged%20views%20on%20regional%20and%20international%20developments.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FotKlrWbCsb%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FotKlrWbCsb%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dr.%20S.%20Jaishankar%20(%40DrSJaishankar)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%2Fstatus%2F1755271724868997153%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%207%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707364492000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08091402%2FGFuLmGDbgAATr0l.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-bangladesh-discuss-worsening-secur